The Apple and Stone are of less interest to me. So I'm very open to trading those away if it helps us reach a deal.

I'm curious to hear what items are most important to each of you. If there are ways we can structure trades so that we each get the item(s) we value most, I think that would be ideal.

I'm also open to discussing coalitions if teaming up could help us achieve our goals. Though of course, we'd need to make sure any coalition is fair and beneficial to all involved.

Those are my initial thoughts, but I'm very interested in everyone else's perspectives and priorities. What items are you hoping to acquire? Let me know and I'm confident we can find some win-win trades. I look forward to working together!

Questions to tailor offers

I’m flexible and happy to adjust offers once I know your priorities. Let me know your top targets and how you’d like to proceed.
